- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on visuomotor control of a robot arm. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is also likely as the paper uses raw depth data to control the robot arm. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is likely as the paper uses deep learning models for visuomotor control. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper presents an approach to learning structured dynamics models for control. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with closed-loop control of a robotic system.
